                    <h2>Nina Anderson</h2>
                    <p>Nina publishes illustrations of books since she was 18.<br /><br />By now, at the age of 21, she has seven publications. They are:</p>
                    <h2>Livros</h2>
                    <p>A Treaty on Toys for Quiet Children from the City<br />Alice<br />Supermagnet and the Sea<br />The Girl that Never Finished Anything<br />Uh-0h!<br />Eight Eating Cookies, Ten eating pastry<br />ABC of Water<br />Was born in São Paulo, Brazil, in 1992 and studied in the Art Institute of São Paulo State’s University.<br /><br />She has traveled Brazil since she was a child and throughout Europe since she was 17 observing all the art and culture around and drawing always in a different way.<br /><br /><b><a href="#">www.cargocollective.com/ninaanderson</a></b></p>
                </div>
